NAME
    mylist2mp3

DESCRIPTION
    Convert registered movies on NicoVideo's mylist to MP3 files with appropriate MP3 tags.

INSTALLATION
    On Debian/Ubuntu :
        $ git clone git://github.com/punytan/mylist2mp3.git
        $ sudo apt-get install ffmpeg

    On Windows :
        Download and uncompress zip/tar file.
        Download and set the path to ffmpeg from http://tirnanog.fate.jp/mirror/ffmpeg/

USAGE
    $ perl mylist2mp3.pl

    * Input the mylist number
    * Input your Email address and password

